<div>Evaluate \( \dfrac{w}{5}-\dfrac{2}{3} \) if \( w=5 \)</div>

\[
\begin{align*}
&=\dfrac{5}{5}-\dfrac{2}{3} \\
&=1-\dfrac{2}{3} \\
&=\dfrac{1}{3}
\end{align*}
\]

